COPS in Emzinoni, Bethal, need help to trace the relatives of Dingaan Malinga. According to police spokeswoman Constable Cynthia Mtshweni, Dingaan (62) was found dead in his shack at Extension 13 squatter camp last week. Mtshweni said Dingaan’s family is believed to be in Embalenhle, and cops need SunReaders’ help to trace them. She urged anyone who knows Dingaan’s relatives to contact Detective Constable Buthelezi on 079 415 4261.